'''MCS''' was a [[Computer/Legends|computer]] technology [[Company/Legends|company]] that focused on the manufacturing of mainframe units.

==History==
While the [[Galactic War]] between the [[Sith Empire (Post–Great Hyperspace War)|reconstituted Sith Empire]] and the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]] took place, the firm arranged a competition for [[Slicer/Legends|slicers]]. With this contest, MCS tried to figure out which one of the competitors could dismantle their newest and best product the quickest. It was probably a marketing-sketch for MCS to prove that their products are unsliceable.<ref name="Mission">{{TORcite|type=crewskill|Slicing|Unsliceable?}}</ref>

During the early days of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]], it went out of business.

